The paper discusses the use of deep learning systems in safety-critical applications, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new method for detecting anomalous image data, which falls under the category of anomaly detection (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of autoencoders, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
